  "texts": [
    "(Appendix 3).",
    "Material 3.",
    "ChatGPT Usage Intention Scale was used to assess the participants' attitudes towards using ChatGPT in educational settings.",
    "This scale is adapted from the AI Technology Instructional Use Intention Scale developed by Chai et al. (2021).",
    "It is also a Likert-type self-report questionnaire consisting of three items."
  ]
}